### Задание 5.3 — Изменить триггер DELETE для orders

При удалении заказа — удалять заказчиков без заказов.

```sql
DROP TRIGGER IF EXISTS after_orders_delete;

DELIMITER //
CREATE TRIGGER after_orders_delete
AFTER DELETE ON orders
FOR EACH ROW
BEGIN
    -- Пишем в лог
    INSERT INTO logs (table_name, operation, log_datetime, current_user)
    VALUES ('orders', 'DELETE', NOW(), USER());
    
    -- Удаляем заказчиков у которых больше нет заказов
    DELETE FROM customers
    WHERE customer_id NOT IN (
        SELECT DISTINCT customer_id FROM orders
    );
END //
DELIMITER ;

-- Проверка:
SELECT * FROM customers;
DELETE FROM orders WHERE order_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM customers;
```

